  "title": "Site Supervisor (ECMO Licensed) - URGENT -  $3,500 - $4,500",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Site Supervisor (ECMO Licensed)</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>Email : HR@ppsjob.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Visit www.ppsjob.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Salary range: $3,500 - $4,500</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The Site Supervisor should have at least 3 years of experience in Construction site supervision of sub\u0002contractors and workers. This individual will be responsible on site for all construction and progress issues.</p>\n<p>Job Highlights</p>\n<p> Work location at many sites in SIngapore</p>\n<p> Must possess ECMO Licence</p>\n<p> Able to start work at short notice</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Principle Duties and Responsibilities:</p>\n<p>• day-to-day coordination to manage the execution and scheduling of project</p>\n<p>• on site supervision of sub-Contractors and maintain their progress;</p>\n<p>• close liaison with the Project Manager to ensure the smooth running of project</p>\n<p>• ensure necessary inspections are made of completed works</p>\n<p>• must be well rounded with all general elements of Construction</p>\n<p>• identify and contribute to the resolutions of problems; work closely with all members of the project</p>\n<p>team to resolve complex issues</p>\n<p>• must have a high regard for SAFETY and be an ambassador of co’s Safety Culture. Lead and</p>\n<p>live companys injury-free environment culture</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Qualifications</p>\n<p>We are looking for a flexible, detail-oriented team player with the ability to manage multiple tasks, manage</p>\n<p>project teams, produce quality work, and consistently meet deadlines. The successful candidate will</p>\n<p>possess:</p>\n<p>• Excellent listening skills and strong communication skills</p>\n<p>• Ability to identify and resolve complex issues</p>\n<p>• Ability to create and support team morale</p>\n<p>• A strong work ethic and a “can-do” attitude</p>\n<p>• Proficient computer skills</p>\n<p>• 3+ years of experience in Construction Site Supervision role, preferably with</p>\n<p>Structural/Mechanical/Electrical background</p>\n<p>• GCE ‘O’ Level/Nitec/relevant education</p>\n<p>• Possess BCSS &amp; Work-at-height Certificate</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>People who succeed aPeople who succeed in the company are:</p>\n<p>• Honest and trustworthy</p>\n<p>• Self-aware and personable</p>\n<p>• Humble, patient and selfless</p>\n<p>• Open, imaginative and creative</p>\n<p>• Positive, energetic and with a sense of urgenct DPR are: • Honest and trustworthy • Self-aware and personable • Humble, patient and selfless • Open, imaginative and creative • Positive, energetic and with a sense of urgenc</p>",
